{"tid":106172,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［PS4][Dark Soul 3]邊個夠我廢","createTime":"2017-02-03T12:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T12:58:24.000Z","uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a213a3f2b3fac4e66bf732960ec28073d50e24ef","tid":106172,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"啱啱交收完隻Dark Soul 3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （早兩個鐘頭嘅事）<br />\n買左個飯返屋企就入碟等Update <br />\n其實自己本身對呢個系列係零認識 但上Youtube見到多左呢隻嘅gameplay之後 斬都心諗有無咁難呀 就買左返嚟喇<br />\n入到新手教學 因為唔太熟啲掣所以比啲小怪殺左一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後去到打灰爐審判者 仆你個街死左十次有多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常一隻遊戲如果比左咁嘅挫折自己 就好易令人放棄 但點撚知 我繼續玩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁總算都打完第一個boss 就行左入去嗰個祭祀場道 同左木匠 矇眼女傾計 之後發現仲坐左個騎士&mdash;霍克伍德喺道 就突然屎忽痕拎刀劈佢 點知佢還手仲要我唔夠抽<br />\n無錯我又死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最估唔到我respawn 之後佢都繼續斬我<br />\n如是者死左三次 我終於打低埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日玩住咁多先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw無可否認Darksoul 係會上癮嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006a6a6efa1f55d994ce091d865265056fb4a852","tid":106172,"uid":9125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"第一隻ps4 game就係佢，每晚收工就開嚟打，打到拎埋白金，好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35a4a9522ef83e2b2bcc4f79600b18444fc1653","tid":106172,"uid":66877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:27:22.000Z","msg":"你不如打埋 祭祀場出面 隻日本刀武士先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw巴打唔洗灰，之黎2隻王都係易打。"},{"pid":"39e339f3b120539032fd6db33f354b6900e129f1","tid":106172,"uid":3179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:30:39.000Z","msg":"我發覺呢隻game 既新手全撚部都唔會舉盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇親啲直播 第一次玩都唔會舉盾<br />\n淨係look 走去避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6489cf6f36e4968d7e7feff9f06c6b43bf4756be","tid":106172,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:59:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一隻ps4 game就係佢，每晚收工就開嚟打，打到拎埋白金，好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n白金要玩好撚多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a4229bb34f9ac7c7f6350a55ee28233da05a22","tid":106172,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我發覺呢隻game 既新手全撚部都唔會舉盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇親啲直播 第一次玩都唔會舉盾<br />\n淨係look 走去避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDs3唔舉盾都得"},{"pid":"a693e2b86346809b39cdd6784fa3807ead0ae9a5","tid":106172,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:33:33.000Z","msg":"玩ds都咁 玩bloodborne你會唔想做人"},{"pid":"6c69f50a1c77d6c4702f69ec51714c0c416ff31c","tid":106172,"uid":29739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T12:41:17.000Z","msg":"屌 我之前玩又係手癢斬咗嗰騎士幾下   點知佢咁撚小氣還拖 不過我又唔夠抽 唯有重開save再打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb47c151b9c3e67630dad2435133f4cb061ab5f","tid":106172,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T12:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩ds都咁 玩bloodborne你會唔想做人</blockquote><br